query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('aggregate-functions',
'android-service',
'graphql',
'mpi',
'navbar',
'network-programming',
'qt5',
'queue',
'sequence',
'shared-libraries',
'timeout',
'timezone',
'transform',
'widget',
'windows-7');
